      "title": "Setup Authentication System",
      "description": "Implement authentication functionality for pentesters including login, logout, and integration with the existing authentication system",
      "details": "Integrate with the existing authentication system used by the admin dashboard. Implement login form, session management, and JWT token handling. Support two-factor authentication. Ensure secure session management with proper token expiration and refresh mechanisms. Use existing authentication endpoints as specified in section 4.1.1 of the PRD.",
      "testStrategy": "Unit tests for authentication components. Integration tests with the backend authentication API. Test login flow with valid and invalid credentials. Test 2FA functionality. Test session persistence and timeout behavior. Security testing for authentication vulnerabilities.",
